comment13.text=\r\n\ Removes\ a\ character\ from\ a\ room.\r\n\ (seperate\ from\ enterRoom()\ as\ that\ method\ is\ also\ used\ to\ place\ character\ in\ initial\ room\ when\ they\ are\ created)\r\n
