comment14.text=\r\n\ Moves\ the\ character\ to\ a\ different\ location.\r\n\ Characters\ move\ randomly\ by\ choosing\ a\ random\ exit\ from\ the\ room\ they\ are\ currently\ in\ (ie\ moving\ to\ a\ random\ neighbouring\ room).\r\n
